### [Nehemiah Chapter 2](../../../bib/kjv/neh002.htm#001.md)

[Nehemiah](../../../bib/kjv/neh001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">neh 2:0</span></span>

Overview

[Neh 2:1](../../../bib/kjv/neh002.htm#001.md), Artaxerxes, understanding
the cause of Nehemiah's sadness, sends him with letters and commission
to Jerusalem; [Neh 2:9](../../../bib/kjv/neh002.htm#009.md), Nehemiah, to
the grief of the enemies, comes to Jerusalem; [Neh
2:12](../../../bib/kjv/neh002.htm#012.md), He views secretly the ruins of
the walls; [Neh 2:17](../../../bib/kjv/neh002.htm#017.md), He incites the
Jews to build.

